# Keep the packed .mcpb lean (lesson from the bloated carbon-mcp-claude-extension.mcpb).
# Pack runtime only: dist/, data/ (incl. model-cache + embeddings.bin), manifest.json,
# package.json, and prod node_modules. Before packing: npm ci --omit=dev
# NOTE: @xenova/transformers pulls onnxruntime (~250 MB in node_modules) for offline semantic
# search. That is the bulk of a packed .mcpb. To ship a keyword-only build, drop
# @xenova/transformers + data/{embeddings.bin,embeddings-meta.json,model-cache} — the server
# auto-falls back to keyword search (mode: "keyword").
src/
scripts/
data/source-raw/
data/scraped/
tsconfig.json
.mcp.json
.gitignore
.mcpbignore
evaluation.xml
*.map
node_modules/.cache/
node_modules/typescript/
node_modules/@types/
